headline: Wheels Up Announces Fernando Mendoza as Brand Ambassador
summary: Wheels Up Experience Inc. (NYSE: UP), one of the world's leading providers of on-demand private aviation, today announced that NCAA National Champion and 2025 Heisman Trophy winner Fernando Mendoza is a new addition to the Wheels Up Ambassador community. Recognized as the most accomplished collegiate football player this season, Mendoza represents the next generation of elite athletes whose lives and careers demand flexibility, efficiency, and connectivity across every mode of travel.

headline: Delta Fleet Expansion And Valuation Outlook After Airbus And Boeing Orders
summary: Delta Air Lines (NYSE:DAL) announces large aircraft purchases from Airbus and Boeing, including its first direct Boeing widebody order since 2008. The new orders are aimed at expanding and modernizing Delta's international widebody fleet. At the same time, the company is handling operational disruptions tied to Winter Storm Fern. For you as an investor, the focus with NYSE:DAL is on how these aircraft commitments shape the airline's long haul and international profile over the long term...
